{
  "stem": "20142.7",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were used before as a experimental thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time, the people were calling me idiot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's no such thing existing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "However, the people from the Sonderkommando who were collecting our clothing were talking-- you know what it is, the Sonderkommando what I mentioned.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These are people who were selected from a-- a group of prisoners to conduct certain services during these selections or through the washing or new transport oncoming.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Collecting their clothes, collecting their shoes, and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of them were talking in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were saying, you don't have to worry today about the gas chamber because they don't have no gas.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were saying to us in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we look at one another and say, let's hope that they know what they are talking about.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when we enter there, these chambers, they told us, when they will be giving you the soap, then you will be convinced.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then the German came out and start distributing the soap among the people as they were entering the chambers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he said, don't worry about your clothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You will get it clean, without any lice, on the other side of the chambers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we somehow were-- were nodding, and thanking him, and getting into the chambers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then we embraced one another, saying, if anything happen, let's at least say goodbye to one another.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And just fortunately, that the water came out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was cold and simple.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But it was so sweet that there is no description of any of such experience in life.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
